Science Boxing Game

2 players.

Rules:
Player 1 starts by answering a question related to science. If player 1 gets
that question right, the other player loses 1 point of health. If player 1 gets
that question wrong, nothing happens. Play then shifts to player 2, who is
presented another question, and attacks player 1 in the same way. Play
continues until one of the players loses all their health, in which the other
player is the winner.
